snippet.title: The Monster Breeder gameplay video 1
snippet.description: Developer plays. It is an early game video that shows the first 12 turns until the completion of the Guild's entry quest. Creation of Panther-Hyena hybrids, Catacomb fight, Arena combat. Voiceover by Colm.
